Application Name- OWASP Juice Shop
Operating System:- Kali Linux (Vm Ware)
Purpose:- OWASP juice shop is an intentionally vulnerable web application is is used for practicing the OWASP Top 10 Web Vulnerability.

Step 1. Run sudo apt update to update all local packages.
step 2. Run sudo apt install docker.io (to download the docker).
step 3. Run sudo systemctl enable docker --now (Our docker automatically starts whenever our system boots).
step 4. To check the status of docker service by:- sudo systemctl status docker
step 5. now Run sudo docker pull bkimminich/juice-shop command
step 6. Now run sudo ocker run --rm -p 3000:3000 bkimminich/juice-shop  command
step 7. Now go to youe browser and put localhost:3000 , your OWASP juice shop is installed in your machine.


